item.dc:creator: @sanga282 sanga282
item.description:
@sanga282 wrote:

[quote=“SomethingToHide, post:9, topic:256719”][quote author=sanga282 link=topic=339061.msg2631238#msg2631238 date=1232187156]

aah dude dont regurgitate the the stuff from the graphics board over here, 1 they dont deserve and 2 it cant go into the RS2 client

Gives them motivation though

Kinda like, if you guys like this stuff you could be making this later on.

you know im indept at C4D im still trying to get texturing right at the moment
[/quote]

Ha. The stuff you don’t do really isn’t hard at all. It just takes the time to try it.

Before I was like dude there’s no way I could do rigging, animation, my own sound effects, or texture my own stuff.

And me and Archer tried rigging one night and it wasn’t too bad. So right now I’m in the middle of making a short movie with a character I’ve modeled, completely textured, rigged, and animated, and then I’m making the sound effects for it.[/quote]
well im practising my modelling as we speak but my texturing skills are just shite lol
